<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="rtl" lang="ar">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8"/>
  <meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
  <title>لوحة الإدارة - إدارة السير الذاتية</title>

  <script src="/theme.js"></script>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Aref+Ruqaa:wght@400;700&family=Tajawal:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:wght,FILL@100..700,0..1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com?plugins=forms,container-queries"></script>

  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      darkMode: "class",
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            primary: "#005A2B",     /* البنفسجي الملكي */
            primaryDark: "#00361A", 
            accent: "#E5B869",      /* الذهب السائل */
            "bg-light": "#F5F3F7",  /* خلفية فاتحة دافئة */
            "bg-dark": "#050505",   /* خلفية داكنة جداً بلمحة بنفسجية */
            "card-light": "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)",
            "card-dark": "rgba(15, 12, 25, 0.8)",
            "border-light": "rgba(0, 90, 43, 0.1)",
            "border-dark": "rgba(229, 184, 105, 0.1)",
          },
          fontFamily: {
            display: ["'Aref Ruqaa'", "serif"],
            sans: ["Tajawal", "sans-serif"],
          },
        }
      }
    };
  </script>

  <style type="text/tailwindcss">
    @layer utilities {
      .scrollbar-hide::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
      .scrollbar-hide { -ms-overflow-style: none; scrollbar-width: none; }
      .glass-panel { @apply backdrop-blur-2xl shadow-xl; }
    }
  </style>

  <style>
    /* تخصيص شريط التمرير */
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; height: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: transparent; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #005A2B; border-radius: 10px; }
    html.dark ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #E5B869; }

    /* حقل البحث الذكي */
    .search-input { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
    .search-input:focus {
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 90, 43, 0.15);
      border-color: #005A2B !important;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    html.dark .search-input:focus {
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(229, 184, 105, 0.15);
      border-color: #E5B869 !important;
    }

    /* صفوف الجدول الديناميكية (Floating Rows) */
    .interactive-row {
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
      border-right: 3px solid transparent;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .interactive-row:hover {
      background: #ffffff !important;
      border-right-color: #005A2B;
      transform: translateX(-4px) scale(1.01);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 90, 43, 0.1);
      z-index: 10;
      position: relative;
    }
    html.dark .interactive-row:hover {
      background: #1A1525 !important;
      border-right-color: #E5B869;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
    }
    .interactive-row:hover td { border-bottom-color: transparent !important; }

    /* شبكة العائلة التفاعلية في الخلفية */
    #nexusCanvas {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
      z-index: 0; pointer-events: auto;
    }

    /* إعدادات أيقونات المظهر */
    html.dark .dark-toggle-icon-moon { display: none; }
    html:not(.dark) .dark-toggle-icon-sun { display: none; }

    /* Mobile Nav */
    #mobileNavOverlay.hidden { display: none; }
    #mobileNavOverlay { display: block; }
    #mobileNavDrawer { transform: translateX(110%); transition: transform .4s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1); }
    #mobileNavDrawer.isOpen { transform: translateX(0); }
  </style>

  <script>
    (function () {
      const saved = localStorage.getItem("theme") || "dark";
      document.documentElement.setAttribute("data-theme", saved);
      document.documentElement.classList.toggle("dark", saved === "dark");
    })();
  </script>

</head>

<body class="bg-bg-light dark:bg-bg-dark text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200 font-sans h-screen flex overflow-hidden selection:bg-accent selection:text-primaryDark">

  <canvas id="nexusCanvas"></canvas>
  <div class="fixed inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-white/40 to-white/80 dark:from-black/40 dark:to-[#050505]/90 pointer-events-none z-[1]"></div>

  <aside class="relative z-20 hidden lg:flex flex-col w-[280px] h-[calc(100vh-2rem)] my-4 mx-4 bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark glass-panel rounded-3xl border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark overflow-hidden shrink-0">
    
    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-6 border-b border-border-light dark:border-border-dark shrink-0">
      <div class="w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-primary dark:bg-accent text-white dark:text-black shadow-lg">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[28px]">shield_person</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-xl leading-none text-primary dark:text-white">عائلة خاشقجي</h1>
        <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mt-1.5">نظام الإدارة المركزية</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <nav class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar p-4 space-y-6">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="px-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">البيانات الرئيسية</p>

        <a href="/admin" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3.5 rounded-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-accent font-bold text-sm transition-colors border border-transparent">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">group</span> إدارة الأفراد
        </a>

        <a href="/admin/pages" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3.5 rounded-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-accent font-bold text-sm transition-colors border border-transparent">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">history_edu</span> إدارة الصفحات
        </a>

        <a href="/admin/honor" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3.5 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 dark:bg-accent/10 text-primary dark:text-accent font-bold text-sm border border-primary/20 dark:border-accent/20 transition-all relative overflow-hidden shadow-sm">
          <div class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-1.5 h-6 rounded-l-full bg-primary dark:bg-accent shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(229,184,105,0.8)]"></div>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">workspace_premium</span> إدارة السير الذاتية
        </a>

        <a href="/admin/news" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3.5 rounded-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-accent font-bold text-sm transition-colors border border-transparent">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">newspaper</span> الأخبار والمناسبات
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="px-3 text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">النظام والموقع</p>
        
        <a href="/admin/support-messages" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3.5 rounded-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-accent font-bold text-sm transition-colors border border-transparent">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">mail</span> رسائل الدعم
        </a>
        
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3.5 rounded-2xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:bg-white dark:hover:bg-white/5 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-accent font-bold text-sm transition-colors border border-transparent">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">account_tree</span> عرض الشجرة
        </a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="p-4 border-t border-border-light dark:border-border-dark shrink-0 m-2 rounded-2xl bg-white/50 dark:bg-black/30">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-cover bg-center border border-gray-200 dark:border-white/10 shadow-sm" style="background-image:url('/assets/default-avatar.png'); background-color: #ddd;"></div>
        <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
          <p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white truncate"><%= locals.admin?.username || "مدير النظام" %></p>
          <p class="text-[10px] text-primary dark:text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mt-0.5 font-bold">Admin</p>
        </div>
        <form method="post" action="/admin/logout" class="m-0">
          <button type="submit" class="w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-red-50 dark:bg-red-500/10 text-red-500 hover:bg-red-500 hover:text-white transition-all shadow-sm" title="تسجيل خروج">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">logout</span>
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <main class="flex-1 flex flex-col min-w-0 h-full relative z-10">
    
    <header class="flex items-center justify-between p-4 lg:p-8 shrink-0">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <button id="mobileNavBtn" class="lg:hidden flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark glass-panel border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark text-primary dark:text-accent shadow-sm" type="button">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">menu</span>
        </button>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold text-primary dark:text-white tracking-tight leading-none mb-1.5">إدارة السير الذاتية</h2>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-gray-500 text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">
            <span>لوحة الإدارة</span>
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">chevron_left</span>
            <span class="text-accent">السير الذاتية</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 shrink-0">
        <button id="themeBtn" class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark glass-panel border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark text-gray-600 dark:text-accent shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform" type="button" title="تبديل المظهر">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px] dark-toggle-icon-moon">dark_mode</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined hidden dark:block text-[24px]">light_mode</span>
        </button>

        <a href="/admin/honor/new" class="flex items-center gap-2 px-6 h-12 rounded-2xl font-bold text-sm bg-primary dark:bg-accent text-white dark:text-black shadow-[0_5px_20px_rgba(58,46,124,0.4)] dark:shadow-[0_5px_20px_rgba(229,184,105,0.20)] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-transform">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[22px]">add</span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">إضافة سيرة</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar px-4 lg:px-8 pb-12">
      <div class="max-w-[100rem] mx-auto space-y-6 lg:space-y-8">

        <section class="bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark glass-panel rounded-[2rem] border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark p-4 md:p-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 shadow-sm">
          <div class="relative w-full md:max-w-md">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-400">search</span>
            <input id="searchInput" type="text" placeholder="بحث بالاسم / المجال / النبذة / الإنجاز..." 
              class="search-input w-full h-12 pr-12 pl-4 bg-white/50 dark:bg-black/20 border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark rounded-xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white placeholder-gray-400 font-bold text-sm focus:ring-0"/>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-[11px] font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 rounded-xl">
            <span>إجمالي السير: <span class="text-primary dark:text-accent text-sm ml-1"><%= items?.length || 0 %></span></span>
            <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-600"></span>
            <span>الترتيب حسب: ORD ثم ID</span>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark glass-panel rounded-3xl shadow-sm border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="absolute top-0 start-0 end-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent via-accent to-transparent opacity-50"></div>
          
          <div class="overflow-x-auto custom-scrollbar p-2 mt-2">
            <table class="w-full min-w-[1120px] text-sm text-right border-separate border-spacing-y-2">
              <thead class="bg-transparent">
                <tr>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] w-20">ID</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] w-24">الصورة</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] w-32">ربط الشجرة</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] min-w-[200px]">الاسم / النبذة</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] min-w-[150px]">المجال</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] min-w-[150px]">التواريخ</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] w-20 text-center">الترتيب</th>
                  <th class="py-3 px-6 font-bold text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest text-[11px] w-32 text-center">إجراءات</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>

              <tbody id="honorTbody">
                <% for (let i=0; i<items.length; i++){ const x = items[i]; %>
                  <tr class="interactive-row group bg-gray-50/50 dark:bg-white/5 border border-transparent border-b-gray-100 dark:border-b-white/5">
                    
                    <td class="py-3 px-6 text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 honor-id rounded-r-xl"><%= x.id %></td>

                    <td class="py-3 px-6">
                      <% const honorPhoto = (x.photo_url && String(x.photo_url).trim()) ? x.photo_url : "/images/default.png"; %>
                      <div class="relative w-12 h-12 rounded-xl overflow-hidden border-2 border-primary/20 dark:border-accent/20 bg-white dark:bg-black shadow-sm">
                        <img src="<%= honorPhoto %>" alt="<%= x.name || '' %>" class="w-full h-full object-cover" onerror="this.src='/images/default.png'"/>
                      </div>
                    </td>

                    <td class="py-3 px-6 text-sm">
                      <% if (x.person_id) { %>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-[11px] font-bold bg-green-100 text-green-700 dark:bg-primary/20 dark:text-green-400">
                          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">link</span>
                          <%= x.person_id %>
                        </span>
                      <% } else { %>
                        <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-[11px] font-bold bg-gray-200 text-gray-600 dark:bg-white/10 dark:text-gray-400">
                          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px]">link_off</span>
                          غير مربوط
                        </span>
                      <% } %>
                    </td>

                    <td class="py-3 px-6">
                      <div class="flex flex-col">
                        <span class="font-bold text-base text-gray-900 dark:text-white group-hover:text-primary dark:group-hover:text-accent transition-colors honor-name"><%= x.name %></span>

                        <% if (x.bio) { %>
                          <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mt-0.5 line-clamp-1 honor-bio"><%= x.bio %></span>
                        <% } else { %>
                          <span class="hidden honor-bio"></span>
                        <% } %>

                        <% if (x.achievement) { %>
                          <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-primary/70 dark:text-accent/70 mt-1 line-clamp-1 honor-achievement"><%= x.achievement %></span>
                        <% } else { %>
                          <span class="hidden honor-achievement"></span>
                        <% } %>
                      </div>
                    </td>

                    <td class="py-3 px-6 text-sm font-bold text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 honor-field">
                      <%= x.field || "-" %>
                    </td>

                    <td class="py-3 px-6">
                      <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] text-primary dark:text-accent">child_care</span>
                          <span class="honor-birth-date"><%= x.birth_date || "-" %></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
                          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[14px] text-gray-400">psychology</span>
                          <span class="honor-death-date"><%= x.death_date || "-" %></span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="hidden honor-birth-place"><%= x.birth_place || "-" %></div>
                      </div>
                    </td>

                    <td class="py-3 px-6 text-center">
                      <span class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-w-[28px] h-7 rounded-lg text-[11px] font-black bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:bg-accent/10 dark:text-accent honor-ord">
                        <%= x.ord %>
                      </span>
                    </td>

                    <td class="py-3 px-6 text-center rounded-l-xl">
                      <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 opacity-100 lg:opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
                        
                        <a href="/honor<%= x.person_id ? ('?personId=' + x.person_id) : '' %>" target="_blank"
                           class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-[#111] border border-gray-200 hover:border-green-500 text-gray-600 hover:text-green-600 dark:border-white/10 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:border-green-500/50 dark:hover:text-green-400 transition-all shadow-sm hover:scale-105" title="عرض في الموقع">
                          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">visibility</span>
                        </a>

                        <a href="/admin/honor/<%= x.id %>/edit" 
                           class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-[#111] border border-gray-200 hover:border-primary text-gray-600 hover:text-primary dark:border-white/10 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:border-accent dark:hover:text-accent transition-all shadow-sm hover:scale-105" title="تعديل">
                          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">edit_square</span>
                        </a>

                        <form method="post" action="/admin/honor/<%= x.id %>/delete" class="m-0" onsubmit="return confirm('هل أنت متأكد من حذف هذا العنصر؟');">
                          <button type="submit" 
                                  class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-white dark:bg-[#111] border border-gray-200 hover:border-red-500 text-gray-600 hover:text-white hover:bg-red-500 dark:border-white/10 dark:text-gray-400 dark:hover:border-red-500/50 dark:hover:text-red-400 transition-all shadow-sm hover:scale-105" title="حذف">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">delete</span>
                          </button>
                        </form>
                        
                      </div>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                <% } %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <div class="px-6 py-4 bg-gray-50/50 dark:bg-white/5 border-t border-border-light dark:border-border-dark flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-primary dark:text-accent mt-0.5">lightbulb</span>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
              تلميح: غيّر قيمة <b class="text-gray-800 dark:text-white">ord</b> لعمل ترتيب العناصر في صفحة السير الذاتية. السيرة المربوطة بشخص من الشجرة يمكن فتحها مباشرة من زر العرض.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</div>

<aside id="mobileNavDrawer" class="fixed top-0 right-0 h-full w-[320px] max-w-[85vw] bg-card-light dark:bg-card-dark glass-panel border-l border-border-light dark:border-border-dark z-[90] flex flex-col">
  <div class="h-1.5 w-full bg-primary"></div>
  <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 border-b border-border-light dark:border-border-dark shrink-0">
    <div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-xl leading-none text-primary dark:text-white">عائلة خاشقجي</h1>
      <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-500 dark:text-accent uppercase tracking-widest mt-1.5">نظام الإدارة</p>
    </div>
    <button id="mobileNavClose" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 hover:text-primary dark:hover:text-accent transition-colors" type="button">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[24px]">close</span>
    </button>
  </div>

  <nav class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar p-6 space-y-3 text-sm font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
    <a href="/admin" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400">group</span> إدارة الأفراد</a>
    <a href="/admin/pages" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-4 rounded-2xl border border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400">history_edu</span> إدارة الصفحات</a>
    <a href="/admin/honor" class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-4 rounded-2xl bg-primary/10 dark:bg-accent/10 text-primary dark:text-accent transition-colors border border-primary/20 dark:border-accent/20"><span class="material-symbols-outlined">workspace_premium</span> السير الذاتية</a>
